{"title":"Java中floorMod方法的理解","date":"2020-02-28T06:11:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月28日","L":"2020/02/28","MM-DD":"02-28"},"author":"Clever Anastasia","thumbnail":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/10/GTxOT1.jpg","link":"2020/02/28/java02","comments":true,"tags":["Java","To be professional"],"categories":["Java"],"updated":"2020-05-10T14:29:12.380Z","content":"<h2><span id=\"概念对比\">概念对比</span></h2>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>名称</th>\n<th>含义</th>\n<th>示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>%</td>\n<td>求余(rem)</td>\n<td>(+4 % -3)== +1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>floorMod()</td>\n<td>取模(mod)</td>\n<td>floorMod(+4,-3)== -2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2><span id=\"本质区别\">本质区别</span></h2>\n<p>对于整型数a，b来说，取模运算或者求余运算的方法都是：<br>\n1.求 整数商： c = a/b;<br>\n2.计算模或者余数： r = a - c*b.</p>\n<p>求模运算和求余运算在第一步不同: <strong>取余运算在取c的值时，向0方向舍入；而取模运算在计算c的值时，向负无穷方向舍入</strong>。</p>\n<p>例：</p>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"padding:0\"></th>\n<th>+4 % -3</th>\n<th>floorMod(+4,-3)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>a=</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>b=</td>\n<td>-3</td>\n<td>-3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>c=</td>\n<td><strong>-1</strong></td>\n<td><strong>-2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>r=</td>\n<td>+1</td>\n<td>-2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2><span id=\"巧记\">巧记</span></h2>\n<p>当a,b同号时，求余运算与取模运算结果相同，符号与a（被除数）相同；否则，取模运算的符号与b（除数）相同。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"“Error:(1, 1) java:非法字符‘\\ufeff’”错误解决办法","link":"2020/03/06/java03"},"next":{"title":"换行与回车的区别","link":"2020/02/27/zaliang02"},"plink":"https://venanastasia.github.io/2020/02/28/java02/","toc":[{"id":null,"title":"概念对比","index":"1"},{"id":null,"title":"本质区别","index":"2"},{"id":null,"title":"巧记","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Clever Anastasia","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International"}}